ia Tabs</a> and <a href="http://www.designchemical.com/blog/index.php/premium-wordpress-plugins/premium-wordpress-plugin-social-network-tabs/" class="external underline">WordPress Social Network Tabs</a> now includes the Instagram API, bringing the total number of supported networks to 17 with 49 feed options!</p>\n<h3>Instagram Tab Feed Options</h3>\n<p><img src="http://www.designchemical.com/media/images/instagram_api_feed_tab.jpg" alt="Instagram Feed Tab" class="img-right hide-excerpt" /></p>\n<ul class="content-list">\n<li>Show an Instagram user feed</li>\n<li>Search Instagram tags</li>\n<li>Show an Instagram Location ID feed</li>\n<li>Search by latitude/longitude + distance</li>\n<li>Show post likes with user thumbnail avatar</li>\n<li>Show latest comments</li>\n<li>Select image size &#8211; 306 px, 150 px or 612 px</li>\n</ul>\n<p>In addition to the Instagram update the plugin now includes the ability to display twitter search feeds and options to disable both retweets and twitter replies.</p>\n<h3>View The Plugin Demos</h3>\n<ul class="content-list">\n<li><a href="http://www.designchemical.com/blog/index.php/premium-jquery-plugins/jquery-social-media-tabs-plugin/" class="underline">jQuery Social Media Tabs</a></li>\n<li><a href="http://www.designchemical.com/blog/index.php/premium-wordpress-plugins/premium-wordpress-plugin-social-network-tabs/" class="underline">Social Network Tabs for WordPress</a></li>\n</ul>\n<h3>Purchase From Codecanyon</h3>\n<ul class="content-list">\n<li><a href="http://codecanyon.net/item/jquery-social-media-tabs/1932796?ref=designchemical" rel="nofollow" class="external underline">jQuery Social Media Tabs</a></li>\n<li><a href="http://codecanyon.net/item/social-network-tabs-for-wordpress/1982987?ref=designchemical" rel="nofollow" class="external underline">Social Network Tabs for WordPress</a></li>\n</ul>\n<div class="feedflare">\n<a href="http://feeds.feedburner.com/~ff/DesignChemical?a=sr4nKXO7Jj4:rXf3IIEAvAk:V_sGLiPBpWU"><img src="