"0"></img></a> <a href="http://feeds.feedburner.com/~ff/DesignChemical?a=gGKMyA62m0s:tohuNaRR9WA:qj6IDK7rITs"><img src="http://feeds.feedburner.com/~ff/DesignChemical?d=qj6IDK7rITs" border="0"></img></a> <a href="http://feeds.feedburner.com/~ff/DesignChemical?a=gGKMyA62m0s:tohuNaRR9WA:yIl2AUoC8zA"><img src="http://feeds.feedburner.com/~ff/DesignChemical?d=yIl2AUoC8zA" border="0"></img></a> <a href="http://feeds.feedburner.com/~ff/DesignChemical?a=gGKMyA62m0s:tohuNaRR9WA:-BTjWOF_DHI"><img src="http://feeds.feedburner.com/~ff/DesignChemical?i=gGKMyA62m0s:tohuNaRR9WA:-BTjWOF_DHI" border="0"></img></a>\n</div><img src="http://feeds.feedburner.com/~r/DesignChemical/~4/gGKMyA62m0s" height="1" width="1"/>";}i:22;a:14:{s:5:"title";s:58:"New WordPress Theme – Caprice Business & Portfolio Theme";s:4:"link";s:61:"http://feedproxy.google.com/~r/DesignChemical/~3/xPfGMUA-8E4/";s:8:"comments";s:124:"http://www.designchemical.com/blog/index.php/wordpress-themes/new-wordpress-theme-caprice-business-portfolio-theme/#comments";s:7:"pubdate";s:31:"Wed, 11 Jan 2012 16:37:49 +0000";s:2:"dc";a:1:{s:7:"creator";s:5:"Admin";}s:8:"category";s:43:"Wordpress ThemesjQuerylayoutthemeswordpress";s:4:"guid";s:42:"http://www.designchemical.com/blog/?p=2588";s:11:"description";s:718:"<p class="text-center"><img src="/media/images/caprice_theme.jpg" alt="Caprice WordPress Theme" class="img-border" /></p>\n<p>Caprice is a modern, elegant and clean WordPress theme, suitable for businesses, portfolios and personal blogs. Added features include Social media pages/shortcodes, which allow you to create content pages directly from your twitter, flickr, dribbble, last.fm or tumblr feeds. Combined with the built-in social share button features and facebook API widgets, Caprice offers excellent opportunities to integrate with your social  &#8230; <a href="http://www.designchemical.com/blog/index.php/wordpress-themes/new-wordpress-theme-caprice-business-portfolio-theme/" class="read_more">more</a></p>";s:7:"content";a:1:{s:7:"encoded";s:4508:"<p class="text-center"><img src="/media/images/caprice_theme.jpg" alt="Caprice WordPress Theme" class="img-border" /></p>\n<p>Caprice is a modern, elegant and clean WordPress theme, suitable for businesses, portfolios and personal blogs. Added features include Social media pages/shortcodes, which allow you to create content pages directly from your twitter, flickr, dribbble, last.fm or tumblr feeds. Combined with the built-in social share button features and facebook API widgets, Caprice offers excellent opportunities to integrate with your social networks.</p>\n<h3>70+ Built-In Shortcodes &#038; jQuery Features</h3>\n<p>Caprice is jQuery enhanced and includes over 70 built-in shortcodes with a shortcode generator, which make creating any layout easy. </p>\n<p>The theme also includes jQuery masonry portfolios, a video/image showcase which is created automatically from your portfolio, evolution sliders with 10+ effects as well as a 3D Flash slider, 3 or 4 column elegant pricing table, option to use Facebook Comments, rich styling elements such as buttons, tabs, toggle, pricing table, testimonials, typography, service icons etc, and much more &#8230;</p>\n<p>Check out the <a href="http://themes.designchemical.com/#caprice" class="external underline">Caprice live preview site</a>, including online style switcher or purchase from <a href="http://www.mojo-themes.com/item/caprice-wordpress-business-portfolio-theme/?r=designchemical" rel="nofollow" class="external underline">mojo themes</a>.</p>\n<h3>Caprice WordPress Theme Features</h3>\n<ul class="content-list">\n<li>WordPress 3.0+ with menus &#038; featured images</li>\n<li>A clean &#038; flexible design</li>\n<li>4 portfolio layouts</li>\n<li>Slick jQuery masonry portfolio with category filters</li>\n<li>Showcase feature &#8211; single page portfolio with individual sliders</li>\n<li>Easy color change via the options panel</li>\n<li>70+ shortcodes</li>\n<li>Built-in shortcode generator for text editors</li>\n<li>19 header fonts options using @font-face</li>\n<li>Custom slider posts with drag/drop order</li>\n<li>2 different slider types including evolution &#038; 3D Flash slider</li>\n<li>Shortcodes for social buttons &#8211; facebook, twitter, linkedin, digg, stumbleupon, google plus one &#038; pin it button</li>\n<li>Add Twitter, flickr, Dribbble, Last.fm or Tumblr feeds</li>\n<li>Sidebar generator</li>\n<li>Contact form generator with jQuery validation and AJAX submit</li>\n<li>jQuery PrettyPhoto lightbox gallery</li>\n<li>Rich styling options: Tabs, toggle, tables, Buttons, boxes, images, Lists, Pricing Table, Testimonials, Typography elements &#038; a complete Service icons set</li>\n<li>Layered and grouped PSDs included</li>\n<li>Valid xHTML</li>\n<li>Thorough help documentation &#038; technical support</li>\n</ul>\n<h3>Live Preview Site</h3>\n<p><a href="http://themes.designchemical.com/#caprice" class="external">http://themes.designchemical.com/#caprice</a></p>\n<h3>Purchase Caprice WordPress Theme</h3>\n<p><a href="http://www.mojo-themes.com/item/caprice-wordpress-business-portfolio-theme/?r=designchemical" rel="nofollow" class="external">Purchase from mojo themes</a></p>\n<div class="feedflare">\n<a href="http://feeds.feedburner.com/~ff/DesignChemical?a=xPfGMUA-8E4:ePz3CaWv0tI:V_sGLiPBpWU"><img src="http://feeds.feedburner.com/~ff/DesignChemical?i=xPfGMUA-8E4:ePz3CaWv0tI:V_sGLiPBpWU" border="0"></img></a> <a href="http://feeds.feedburner.com/~ff/DesignChemical?a=xPfGMUA-8E4:ePz3CaWv0tI:F7zBnMyn0Lo"><img src="http://feeds.feedburner.com/~ff/DesignChemical?i=xPfGMUA-8E4:ePz3CaWv0tI:F7zBnMyn0Lo" border="0"></img></a> <a href="http://feeds.feedburner.com/~ff/DesignChemical?a=xPfGMUA-8E4:ePz3CaWv0tI:gIN9vFwOqvQ"><img src="http://feeds.feedburner.com/~ff/DesignChemical?i=xPfGMUA-8E4:ePz3CaWv0tI:gIN9vFwOqvQ" border="0"></img></a> <a href="http://feeds.feedburner.com/~ff/DesignChemical?a=xPfGMUA-8E4:ePz3CaWv0tI:qj6IDK7rITs"><img src="http://fee